
Setup before you start on P4b:

1. Download and extract file, “P4b” into your Ubuntu

2. Next, copy “darkworld.launch” file under the launch folder

3. Navigate to src >> turtlebot3_simulations >> turtlebot3_gazebo >> launch

4. Paste copied launch file in this folder

5. Next, copy “darkworld.world” file under the world folder

6. And navigate to src >> turtlebot3_simulations >> turtlebot3_gazebo >> worlds

7. Paste copied world file in this folder


